WH.N
Wyndham Hotels & Resorts, Inc.
Consumer Discretionary
Wyndham AI is driving more direct bookings, reducing front desk workloads that's accelerating significant
ancillary revenues for thousands of our hotel owners through automatic upsell opportunities like early
check-ins, late check-outs, and in-room amenity upgrades. To-date, Wyndham AI has already handled
more than 0.5 million customer interactions, delivering faster service, higher booking conversion, and a
25% reduction in average handle time, all contributing to nearly 300 basis points of improvement in direct
contribution for hotels leveraging Wyndham AI to its fullest potential.
